  <trk>
    <name>307 Wispile - Chrine - Lauenensee - Lauenen</name>
    <desc>Hike along the ridge of the Wispile and enjoy the panoramic view over the Saanenland and the view to our 3000-meter peaks. Almost at the end of the path, the famous Lauenensee awaits you.</desc>
